                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Problem 1. Let "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "X"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "be an essentially bounded random variable with mean zero. Show that "
