                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "X"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "in the two groups. After an acceptable allocation is found, outcome variables will be measured, and their means will be compared in group A and group B to estimate a treatment effect. "
