                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "N"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "), this plan will result in unbiased estimates of the A versus B casual effect based on the sample means of "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "Y"
                    },
